 little bit shorter.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t- Full exhalation is essential\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LlxtPicx6H8\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t- 4-6/10 harmstring contraction\n\t\t\t- Referenced position + muscle integration\n\t\t\t\t- 90/90 hip lift with hip shift\n\t\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YoSf3OFpPp4\n\t\t\t\t- Sitting exercise\n\t\t\t\t\t- https://youtu.be/uYtLHHT1AhU?t=382\n\t\t\t\t- Ab exercises\n\t\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uy4u23pzm3E&list=PLFq2zv7d_8BDM_v72NSdA1Dg2IRjZuZrb&index=13\n\t\t\t- Removing references + integration\n\t\t\t\t- Band exercises\n\t\t\t\t\t- https://youtu.be/xq0hXN5mAxY\n\t\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DGR_xH0wHrY&t=471s\n\t\t\t\t- Gait Mechanics\n\t\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cnNZ8YSaq74&list=PLFq2zv7d_8BDM_v72NSdA1Dg2IRjZuZrb&index=15\n\t\t\t- Loaded integration\n\t\t\t\t- https://youtu.be/Tsa-NaWpPxY?si=C5ZDspIxBz-yHhGz\n\t\t\t\t- Loaded integration in [starting] upright position\n\t\t\t\t\t- Squat\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- Deep Squat\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SdaqV9mJ_cw&pp=ygUSY29ub3IgaGFycmlzIHNxdWF0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t- Right Hip Shift in a Squat\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t- https://youtu.be/I4hKmqYTpjY?si=LyvyXMn4oFJaBaOQ\n\t- Posture malformations or deformations\n\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ag3DG2UvnI8\n\t\t- Lateral pelvic tilt\n\t\t\t- The Left AIC (anterior interior chain) Pattern\n\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zk2ZRqvlRbo\n\t\t\t\t- Exercises\n\t\t\t- The Right BC (right brachial) Pattern\n\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=471aoJqG5eg\n\t\t\t\t- https://www.conorharris.com/blog/how-to-fix-uneven-shoulders\n\t\t\t- PEC (posterior exterior chain) Pattern\n\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1qOG1v6Yjr8\n\t\t\t- The Right TMCC (temporomandibular cervical chain) Pattern\n\t\t\t\t- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kqQtOd-S_-c&t=6s\n\t\t\t- Wide Infrasternal Angle\n\t\t\t\t- https://www.conorharris.com/blog/a-comprehensive-guide-to-the-